   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>You seem busy today.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-a" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You can't call that an interrogation…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>You fiercely interrogated me the other time to see if I've been trading with the merchants from the south.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-b" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What happened?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>But you sure made me scared and I was determined to let you know if something like this happened!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-c" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(It looks like the flower Casmina brought…)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>I just received an expensive order that you might be interested in! Take a look at this.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Sterope waves a half-dried red petal in front of your eyes.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-d" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, what did the person order?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>This flower only grows in places warmer than Chiron Island. Can you guess who placed the order?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-e" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>…Could that be the reason why you were waiting for me…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Lobster claws and blue pearls! They are actually quite hard to get…<BR>Chiron Beach is the only place where I can get them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-f" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Really…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>I'm an honest merchant! I'll pay you handsomely for your services and I can let you continue trading with the merchant if you want. It's not a bad deal.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-1-g" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll think about it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>
I could have asked you to get the goods for me and sold them to the trader myself. But I thought you could get the information you want by creating direct connections with the people from the south.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-2" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(I should ask Vernicka for his opinion.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Okay, but I won't wait for long. Traders don't wait for you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I guess I should just turn it down.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka looks speechless after hearing what you said.)</FONT><BR>Don't tell me you're here to register yourself as a merchant of Merca.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>But trading with an unknown stranger at times like this would be…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>Nonsense. I'm just speechless that you're asking me for advice when it's plain good opportunity.<BR>It's up to you to decide, but why aren't you grabbing this lucky chance?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I thought I'd already finished weighing the pros and cons.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>Opportunities don't wait for conditions to become favourable. You should never forget that the more weights on a merchant's scale the better. Whether it's Anti-Goddess Faction, Rhadames, Merca… or even Childs.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I thought you don't need a scale anymore.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>How foolish of you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="55" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(I should go and get the goods.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>……There could be a scale that doesn't budge no matter what happens. But would that be a reason to stop weighing things? You just need more weights on the scale to keep it in balance.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>
I don't expect much from you but good luck anyway.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
